lead_paragraph: Notre Dame coach Brian Kelly reiterated early Sunday that he plans to be back as coach of the Fighting Irish after a 45-27 loss to rival Southern California dropped the Fighting Irish to 4-8, their second-worst record in five decades.

headline.print_headline: Kelly: I'm Not Interested in Options Outside Notre Dame
headline.main: Kelly: I'm Not Interested in Options Outside Notre Dame
